data.description: Priced to Sell, Large 1505 SF 3 Bed 2 Bath Manufactured home on just shy 1/4 Acre lot in Rockport. This home needs some TLC and a buyer willing to put in the sweat equity, but will be well worth it. Home boasts a wide open floor plan with a huge eat in kitchen, vaulted ceilings throughout, dining room and a large den that could also possibly be converted in to a 4th bedroom. Property is fully fenced and has a carport and 12x12 shop. Close to Sauk River and Howard Miller Steelhead park.
